🚀 ASSIGNMENT 3: MAVEN — STEP BY STEP
🔹 Step 1: Create Project Structure

👉 In VS Code create:

project/
 ├── pom.xml
 ├── src/main/java/com/example/App.java
 └── src/test/java/com/example/AppTest.java
🔹 Step 2: Write Code

👉 App.java

public class App {
    public static String grade(int marks){
        if(marks>90) return "A";
        else return "B";
    }
}
🔹 Step 3: Run Maven Commands

👉 In terminal:

mvn compile
mvn test
mvn clean install
🔹 Step 4: Jenkins Pipeline
Jenkins → New Item
Select Pipeline

👉 Paste:

pipeline {
    agent any
    stages {
        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                bat 'mvn clean install'
            }
        }
    }
}

👉 Click Save → Build Now

